parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and hesitation can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded.

symptoms: Windshield wiper linkages are out of sync

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cooling system failure can cause engine overheating, damage, and failure, leading to accidents and injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause battery drain, failure to start, and accidents.
Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly

causing the vehicle to lose power or enter limp home mode.
